    <h1>The Selection Field Type</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p>This Field Type represents a single selection or multiple choice=
s from a list of options.</p>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Name</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Internal name</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Expected input type</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>Selection</code></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>ezselection</code></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>mixed</code></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
