<p></p>
<h2 id=3D"TheSelectionFieldType-Description">Description</h2>
<p>The&nbsp;Selection&nbsp;Field Type&nbsp;stores single selections or mult=
iple choices from a list of options, by populating a hash with the list of =
selected values.</p>
<h2 id=3D"TheSelectionFieldType-Inputexpectations">Input expectations</h2>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Type</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Example</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>array</code></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>array( 1, 2 )</code></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<h2 id=3D"TheSelectionFieldType-Valueobject">Value object</h2>
<h3 id=3D"TheSelectionFieldType-Properties">Properties</h3>
<p>The Value class of this Field Type contains the following properties:</p=
>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Property</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Type</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Description</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>$selection</code></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>int[]</code></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">This property will be used for the list of selec=
tions, which will be a list of integer values, or one single integer value.=
</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;">
<b>Value object content examples</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"brush: php; gutter: false; theme: Eclipse" style=3D"font-size=
:12px;">// Single selection
$value-&gt;selection =3D 1;=20
=20
// Multiple selection
$value-&gt;selection =3D array( 1, 4, 5 ); </pre>=20
</div>
</div>
<h3 id=3D"TheSelectionFieldType-Constructor">Constructor</h3>
<p>The&nbsp;<code>Selection\Value</code>&nbsp;constructor accepts an array =
of selected element identifiers.</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;">
<b>Constructor example</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"brush: php; gutter: false; theme: Eclipse" style=3D"font-size=
:12px;">// Instanciates a selection value with items #1 and #2 selected
$selectionValue =3D new Selection\Value( array( 1, 2 ) );</pre>=20
</div>
</div>
<h3 id=3D"TheSelectionFieldType-Stringrepresentation">String representation=
</h3>
<p>String representation of this Field Type is its list of selections as a =
string, concatenated with a comma.</p>
<p>Example:</p>
<blockquote>
<p><code>"1,2,24,42"</code></p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id=3D"TheSelectionFieldType-Hashformat">Hash format</h2>
<p>Hash format of this Field Type is the same as Value object's <strong><co=
de>selection</code></strong> property.</p>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;">
<b>Example of value in hash format</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"brush: php; gutter: true; theme: Eclipse" style=3D"font-size:=
12px;">$hash =3D array( 1, 2 );</pre>=20
</div>
</div>
<h2 id=3D"TheSelectionFieldType-Validation">Validation</h2>
<p>This Field Type validates the input, verifying if all selected options e=
xist in the field definition and checks if multiple selections are allowed =
in the Field definition.<br>If any of these validations fail, a <code><span=
 class=3D"nx">ValidationError</span></code><span class=3D"p">&nbsp; </span>=
is thrown, specifying the error message, and for the case of the option val=
idation a list with the invalid options is also presented.</p>
<h2 id=3D"TheSelectionFieldType-Settings">Settings</h2>
<hr>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Name</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Type</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Default value</th>
<th class=3D"confluenceTh">Description</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>isMultiple</code></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>boolean</code></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>false</code></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Used to allow or deny multiple selection from th=
e option list.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>options</code></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>hash</code></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd"><code>array()</code></td>
<td class=3D"confluenceTd">Stores the list of options defined in the field =
definition.</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<div class=3D"code panel pdl" style=3D"border-width: 1px;">
<div class=3D"codeHeader panelHeader pdl" style=3D"border-bottom-width: 1px=
;">
<b>Selection Field Type example settings</b>
</div>
<div class=3D"codeContent panelContent pdl">=20
<pre class=3D"brush: php; gutter: false; theme: Eclipse" style=3D"font-size=
:12px;">use eZ\Publish\Core\FieldType\Selection\Type;
=20
$settings =3D array(
    "isMultiple" =3D&gt; true,
    "options" =3D&gt; array(1 =3D&gt; 'One', 2 =3D&gt; 'Two', 3 =3D&gt; 'Th=
ree')
);</pre>=20
</div>
